---
title: "Contact Us | SlashExperts"
description: "Get in touch with SlashExperts — talk to sales, get support, or explore partnerships. Book a demo or email hello@slashexperts.com."
pageCSS: contact
ds7: true
permalink: /contact/
---

{% extends "layouts/base-w.njk" %}

{% block content %}
{% raw %}


  <section class="ct-hero" data-nav-surface="dark">
    <div class="ct-hero__bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="w-container">
      <div class="ct-hero__inner w-reveal">
        <span class="w-badge"><span class="w-badge__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#i-mail"/></svg></span>Contact</span>
        <h1 class="w-display ct-hero__h">Let's start <span class="w-accent">a conversation.</span></h1>
        <p class="w-lead ct-hero__lead">Have questions about how SlashExperts can transform your sales process? Whether you're ready to bring trust into every deal or just exploring what's possible, our team is here to help.</p>
        <div class="ct-hero__actions">
          <a class="w-btn w-btn--primary w-btn--lg" href="/book-a-demo">Book a Demo <svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-arrow-right"/></svg></a>
          <a class="w-btn w-btn--ghost w-btn--lg" href="mailto:hello@slashexperts.com">Email our team <svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-arrow-right"/></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="channels" class="w-section cz-light" data-nav-surface="light">
    <div class="w-container">
      <div class="w-section-head w-reveal">
        <h2 class="w-section-head__title">We'd love to hear from you.</h2>
        <p class="w-section-head__lead">Pick the path that fits — sales, support, or partnerships — and we'll get back to you promptly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-grid w-stagger">
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand ct-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-trending"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Talk to Sales</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Discover how leading B2B companies are accelerating deals by connecting prospects with their happiest customers.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><a class="ct-link" href="/book-a-demo">Book a Demo <svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-arrow-right"/></svg></a></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand ct-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-message"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Customer Support</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Already using SlashExperts? Get help with your account, integrations, or any technical questions from our team.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><a class="ct-link" href="mailto:hello@slashexperts.com">Email support <svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-arrow-right"/></svg></a></div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand ct-card w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-match"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">Partnerships</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">Interested in integrating with SlashExperts or exploring partnership opportunities? Let's build something great together.</p>
          <div class="w-card__foot"><a class="ct-link" href="mailto:hello@slashexperts.com">Start a conversation <svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-arrow-right"/></svg></a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-info w-reveal">
        <span class="ct-info__item"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-mail"/></svg><a href="mailto:hello@slashexperts.com">hello@slashexperts.com</a></span>
        <span class="ct-info__item"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-home"/></svg>San Francisco, CA</span>
        <span class="ct-info__item"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-shield"/></svg><a href="/security">Security &amp; Trust</a></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

{% endraw %}
{% endblock %}
